Entry.JapaneseText: おおっ……なんか緊張するぜ……
だって今おれたち、 女王の住む城に来てるんだぜ？
Entry.EnglishText: Well, haven't we made it into the castle where the Queen lives?

Entry.JapaneseText: 意外ー!! 女王様のコトなんて なんとも思ってないのかと思ったヨ。
Entry.EnglishText: That's unexpected! I never thought you would ever be thinking about the Queen.

Entry.JapaneseText: いや、そうだけどよ……なんかこういう所に 来ると、おごそかな気分にならねーか？
Entry.EnglishText: Well, that's true, but... Doesn't a place like this inspire awe when you enter?

Entry.JapaneseText: ボクは別に……<Blue>王の盾<White>にいた時に、 普通に入ってたし。
Entry.EnglishText: Not really... When I was in the <Blue>Royal Shield<White>, going in was pretty ordinary.
